{"tid":35180,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖）食食下飯有隻蝗蟲仔起隔離賴尿","createTime":"2016-12-12T02:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T02:35:48.000Z","uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3272b64660a751ade6a41b1038f3c338e8484e3","tid":35180,"uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:14:00.000Z","msg":"尋日食食下野有隻蝗蟲仔企起我隔離賴尿<br />\n屌佢老母,佢老母起收銀埋完單就咁拖佢走<br />\n粒聲都唔出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   ,紙巾都係職員擺既<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yoZJ902.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyoZJ902.jpg&h=a7903990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問題黎喇  ,  有冇巴絲可以幫手改走堆紙巾？"},{"pid":"e9443aaa3debe1d6d4d8213fa2f6bb0e10933031","tid":35180,"uid":20210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:15:28.000Z","msg":"元氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e12065f2025260cee1d8e5ca5ef744e93977892","tid":35180,"uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:17:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>元氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀"},{"pid":"be454312df1c305ef4c148f1f9cc30a0c8f96d11","tid":35180,"uid":1044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:20:43.000Z","msg":"失禁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a33d887f9920e0bb1dc6ca820c9ccf65111fa0","tid":35180,"uid":20210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>元氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前返元氣pt 有班蝗黎食飯 我地塞曬佢地坐最入一排<br />\n勁撚嘈又食得污糟都算啦<br />\n成班走左之後 我地執枱<br />\n地下有個膠袋裝住包尿係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲暖添架屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500eb21ee83d44385469ebb064dc019684577fbb","tid":35180,"uid":48143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:35:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>元氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前返元氣pt 有班蝗黎食飯 我地塞曬佢地坐最入一排<br />\n勁撚嘈又食得污糟都算啦<br />\n成班走左之後 我地執枱<br />\n地下有個膠袋裝住包尿係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲暖添架屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第一次親眼遇見蝗蟲仔屎屎尿尿<br />\n果刻唔知佢老母起邊,後來我見d員工話佢賴尿,<br />\n我即刻對住佢講：屌你賴尿 <br />\n佢望一望我就比佢老母拉走  <br />\n唉  好撚痴線"}]}